➜疫情重启再次封国，外贸企业如何应对？
http://www.sohu.com/a/429469830_115514	20570
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201104/85253ffc30494160bf3b2a4b6c9d7c0a.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span><span><strong>疫情强势反弹</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p>据《参考消息》11月3日报道，欧洲近期再次成为疫情暴发震中 ，全球46%的新发病例集中在欧洲，但是有了对抗第一波疫情暴发的经验之后，欧洲各国迅速采取了应对措施，包括英法在内的12个欧洲国家直接宣布“封国”。</p>
<p><strong>英国</strong>：从11月5日开始到12月2日，英格兰地区再次实行全面封锁，除了出售日用品的超级市场外，餐饮、娱乐等非生活必需的设施、机构一律停止营业。</p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>法国：</strong></span></span></span><span><span>从</span>10月30</span><span><span>日起</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>法国再次实施禁运</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>至少</span></span><span><span>要</span></span><span><span>等到</span>12月1日</span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>德国</strong></span></span></span><span><span><span><strong>：</strong></span></span></span><span><span>从</span></span><span>11月2日</span><span><span>起</span></span><span><span>全国</span></span><span>“封城”</span><span><span>一个月</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>全国大部分公共场所</span></span><span><span>、</span></span><span><span>餐饮</span></span><span><span>和</span></span><span><span>娱乐场所</span></span><span><span>被</span></span><span><span>关闭</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>个人旅游</span></span><span><span>被</span></span><span><span>限制</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>意大利</strong></span></span></span><span><span><span>：</span></span></span><span><span>从</span>10月26日到11月24日，</span><span><span>健身房、电影院、游泳池</span></span><span><span>和</span></span><span><span>其他</span></span><span><span>人群聚集的</span></span><span><span>场所同样</span></span><span><span>被</span></span><span><span>要求暂时关闭</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>酒吧、餐馆</span></span><span><span>和</span></span><span><span>其他餐饮场所</span></span><span><span>的</span></span><span><span>营业时间缩短</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>西班牙</strong>：</span></span></span><span><span>到</span></span><span><span>当地</span></span><span>10月29日</span><span><span>为止</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>西班牙只有</span></span><span>4个</span><span><span>大区没有实施限制居民出入</span></span><span><span>的</span></span><span><span>措施</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>其他大区</span></span><span><span>也</span></span><span><span>封锁边界</span></span><span><span>，除</span></span><span><span>不可抗力</span></span><span><span>外，</span></span><span><span>禁止居民自由出入</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>奥地利</strong>：</span></span></span><span><span>从</span>11月3日起，</span><span><span>奥地利</span></span><span><span>将</span></span><span><span>再次实行国家</span></span><span>“</span><span><span>封锁</span></span><span>”。</span></p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>希腊</strong></span></span></span><span><span><span>：</span></span></span><span><span>首都雅典</span></span><span><span>和</span></span><span><span>其他主要城市</span></span><span><span>将在</span></span><span><span>一个月</span></span><span><span>内</span></span><span><span>实施局部</span></span><span>“</span><span><span>封锁</span></span><span>”，</span><span><span>全国范围</span></span><span><span>内</span></span><span><span>实行宵禁</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>又</span></span><span><span>一轮疫情暴发强势反扑</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>无奈之下</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>欧洲各国政府重新开始实施封锁</span></span><span><span>、</span></span><span><span>限制</span></span><span><span>等抗疫</span></span><span><span>措施</span></span><span><span>，以</span></span><span><span>遏制新发肺炎疫情进一步蔓延</span></span><span><span>。</span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span>即使</span></span><span><span>是在</span></span><span><span>此前欧洲</span></span><span><span>最有效的抗疫</span></span><span><span>措施</span></span><span><span>下，</span></span><span><span>德国</span></span><span><span>也</span></span><span><span>开始遭遇疫情反弹</span></span><span><span>。</span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span>进一步恶化</span></span><span><span>的新</span></span><span><span>冠疾病</span></span><span><span>将</span></span><span><span>导致更加严格</span></span><span><span>的</span></span><span><span>限制</span></span><span><span>，给</span></span><span><span>资本市场带来更大</span></span><span><span>的</span></span><span><span>不确定性</span></span><span><span>，也会给</span></span><span><span>经济带来难以迅速平息</span></span><span><span>的</span></span><span><span>干扰</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>事在人为</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>反过来说</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>中国现在</span></span><span><span>最是</span></span><span><span>安全的</span></span><span><span>，也是</span></span><span><span>许多外贸企业崛起</span></span><span><span>的好机会，</span></span><span><span>前提</span></span><span><span>是要</span></span><span><span>做好风险防范</span></span><span><span>！</span></span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span><span><strong>外贸行业可能面临的</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>7</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>个挑战</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>一、订单数量下降。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成因</strong>：</span></span><span>疫情严重影响经济形势，除一般日常食品和医疗用品外，其它产品需求将大幅下降。对外贸易订单量将有所下降。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>对策</strong>：</span></span><span>拓展业务范围，积极与买家沟通，证明交货能力，并与中国高效的疫情控制政策保持一致，消除买家的疑虑。保持采购关系，待疫情结束后，需求将恢复。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>二、取消定单的数量增加。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成因</strong></span></span><span>：需求减少，或国内防疫政策原因不能接货，导致客户取消订单。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>对策</strong>：</span></span><span>稳住客户，建议客户先观望一段时间，一起找出解决办法。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>三</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>、</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>供应链的中断。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成因</strong></span></span><span><strong>：</strong>供应商也可能因为进口原料中断供应等问题</span><span>，</span><span>而影响交货进度。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>对策</strong></span></span><span><strong>：</strong>及时调整供应链细节，随时关注供应链各环节的变化，并与客户</span><span>有效</span><span>沟通。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>四、市场推广渠道受阻。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成因</strong></span></span><span><strong>：</strong>在中国广交会等重要展会上，许多内贸企业也将参加各种国内展会，由于此次疫情持续不断，预计今年国内外贸企业的展会营销将严重受阻。</span><span><span>广交会在经过</span>“非典”之后，成交额从2002年春交会的168亿元下降到了2003年33.12亿元，因疫情而减少的数字，令人震惊！</span></p>
<p><span><span><span><strong>对策</strong>：</span></span></span><span><span>开辟线上推广渠道，建立公司网站，同时采用</span>SEO/SEM,SNS,EDM等线上营销手段。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>五、货物交付困难</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成因</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>：</strong></span></span><span>供货方方面交货时间不确定，港口防疫站的目标政策多变，物流运输成本节节攀升。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>对策</strong></span></span><span>：及时对供应链进行调整，规范供应链各个环节。关心目港防疫工作，提前做好防疫准备。与此同时，可关注其他</span><span>运输方式</span><span>与第三方</span><span>中转</span><span>国的货运渠道。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>六、</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>汇率大幅波动。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成因</strong></span></span><span><span>：</span></span><span><span>在危机爆发的背景下，美联储可能采取</span>“无限制宽松”的政策以应对流动性短缺，而现在正值美国总统大选，部分国家正在与中国展开贸易战。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>对策</strong>：</span></span><span>可与客户协商以人民币结算，或在签约时考虑到汇率因素。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>七、</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>账期长收款难</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>。</strong></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>成</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>因</strong>：</span></span><span><span>过于依赖传统的采集方式。一般而言，做外贸交易的收款结算，比较常用的是电汇、现金结算和西联。这种外贸收款方式一般都有一个特点，就是可以大批量结帐，收款金额大，到账时间一般在</span>3~7天左右，</span><span>国外客户也觉得繁琐</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>对策</strong>：</span></span><span><span>付款凭证</span>(D/P)对出口商有风险，在D/P支付方式下，争取使用大约30%的电汇预付款(T/T)。投保出口信用保险，风险可转嫁。它可以帮助你减少经济损失。</span></p>
<p>（来源：外贸运营说）</p>
